Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:08.44,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(358,294)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}RESIGNATION{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:12.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just because we broke up, why do you have to quit the festival club?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Isn't the festival club an important place where you belong, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:22.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Or is it because you can't stand being in the same club with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:23.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:27.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's an important place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I'm letting you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:34.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're the one who can't be in the same place as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You didn't come to our lecture earlier, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:39.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:40.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:45.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was shaken, and I skipped class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:48.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my fault for being so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:56.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I understand why you broke up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:01:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've accepted that it was the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:05.92,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(300,301)}Last Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:15.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, if we could meet in a dream, could I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:40.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Say, if sadness alone floats down from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:48.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If that kind of voice pains you even now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:52.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if, off to the side, our hands are placed on each other's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:56.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This memory wouldn't fade, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:02:04.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if, when our eyes meet, I can't say the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:08.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your words illuminate the world more than anyone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Next to me, "Goodbye means I love you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't be forthright
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Though I alone sing of loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Thank you means I'm in love with you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:24.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The world's end of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You saw what was on the Okamera, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You saw me go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:48.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you, but my memories have been returning lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When they do, my current memories disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:54.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's what happened at the Awa dance festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:59.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think I'll revert to the former Tada Banri soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:03.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I do, the one living here now will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:08.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You wanted to break up with me because you knew that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:14.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you, Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, I'll never hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:27.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you don't need to distance yourself from our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and you don't need to quit the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can continue being yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:41.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you can act like you've forgotten all about what you and I had,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't quit the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:46.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then we're really broken up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,From now on, we're just friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:55.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can I promise one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:07.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If... If you don't forget me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:16.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I promise I'll never leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I'm being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I'm not making any sense, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But let me promise you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:31.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been looking for Yanagisawa Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He ran off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I chased him, but I lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And Kouko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My answer is "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:59.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you were going to disappear, and asked me to look after Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This world doesn't move according to your wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and you can't make people do what you want them to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Also, don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's Roboko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Roboko's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everyone welcomed us back with smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko revoked her resignation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:35.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and we began preparing for the school festival again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:41.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:44.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san, Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That night, I went to Yana-san's apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I didn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.41,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,111)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}I WANT TO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.41,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(278,204)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}TALK TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.41,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(286,288)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}CALL ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.41,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(308,366)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}- BANRI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The next morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:06:01.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I found the note I'd left for him stuck to my own door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:06.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It must've been his way of saying he wouldn't hear anything I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san also stopped coming to class,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and I couldn't find a chance to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I went back to just being friends with Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:21.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I tried to act as naturally as possible during class and practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.35,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,44)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}DAYS UNTIL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.35,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(359,81)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}THE FUKURAI FESTIVAL:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the school festival was approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The coach will yell at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd rather run outside than do strength training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was I just thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.81,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,44)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}DAYS UNTIL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.81,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(359,81)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}THE FUKURAI FESTIVAL:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What, you didn't review at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:12.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,K-Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait! Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:30.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What did you say to Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She looked like she was going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure everything's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Despite her looks, Kouko is fairly-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, no. I'm talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:55.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't act like I'm not talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You seemed spaced-out earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's been going on with everyone behind my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know something, Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I don't know how much I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:29.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to pry into my friends' secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's a little mean to exclude me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:38.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There are two things I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:43.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san didn't really want to break up with Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:47.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened, but she's really forcing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The other thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I hate the way things are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.16,Dialogue8,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,44)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}DAYS UNTIL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.16,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(359,81)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}THE FUKURAI FESTIVAL:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,On that note!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gather 'round, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaga-san, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,G-good morning, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's all go hang out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We can go to the amusement park again or get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's all meet after class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The school festival's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You remember our pact, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When someone says let's hang out, we all go unconditionally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is one of those times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But there's something going on between me and Yana-san right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Moping around behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because you've been acting like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have to invite everyone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey... Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not making any more of a scene than you usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,On that note, we're going to have an honest talk tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's all get together and lay it all on the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If we don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,our group really will fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:18.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll definitely be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:30.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And I'll explain what's been going on to everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know if Yana-san will come, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:40.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if I have to trick or guilt him into coming, I'll bring Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We should talk things out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:50.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think it's great you'll have a chance to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you want to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go revive your friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, let's do our best tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who am I waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where am I, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I brought him, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I tricked him into coming by telling him it was an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now, let's have a good, honest talk today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:40.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After learning all that so suddenly, it took some time to cool my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But today, I'll listen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko! Kaga Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look! Yanagisawa Mitsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda! Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Help me, Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:14.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda! Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda, I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been waiting to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was keeping an eye on him because I'm worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:06.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll stay at his neighbor Nana-senpai's place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:31.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I saw Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:37.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko was crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko... Kouko was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You don't usually call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:01.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of going to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think my memories from before the accident are returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:10.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And in turn, I feel like my memories since the accident are disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:15.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think I can live here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Should I come get you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:25.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Actually, could you come see the school festival tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The university's cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're doing the Awa dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda's doing it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:37.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your father's working, so I'll come by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:41.00,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(487,261)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}To commemorate the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:41.00,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(487,284)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}anniversary of our escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:41.00,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(488,299)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}From your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:41.00,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(493,330)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Kouko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then... see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:02.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I slept with Nana-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:08.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:09.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:12.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you sleeping in my bed, Nana-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told you last night to sleep with your door unlocked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:19.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I could come help if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And you weren't getting up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I had Nana-senpai go check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were sleeping so peacefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I laid down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:35.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then I just drifted off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have done that, Nana-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Despite how he is, he's still a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"How he is"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, see you later, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good luck with your Awa dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:52.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll be seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:06.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:16.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I haven't told Linda and Nana-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:21.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...that I'm planning to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:26.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wrote a bunch of notes to myself last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.21,Dialogue12,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(202,200)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}KOKO, EX-GIRLFRIEND{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,for after I lose my current memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.32,Dialogue10,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(336,123)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}2D-KUN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.19,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(219,136)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}FESTIVAL CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:35.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Soon, I'm going to forget everything that's happened since the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel certain in that prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.79,Dialogue11,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(241,49)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}86th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.79,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(261,88)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}FUKURAI UNIVERSITY FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kouko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Morning, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just checked in on some other clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}She was crying yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Miss Ultrasonic looked really busy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:12.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Did I forget something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Her upperclassmen are really working her hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't let you go until you smile more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't make those noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's a mean thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A lot has happened, but we overcame it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We overcame it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:18:02.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,From all over Japan, we've gathered here to experience this moment together as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:06.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Dance, dance, and enjoy this miracle with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's prove we're living here in this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, there's nothing left for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you guys have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The president of the private school committee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you couldn't help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:37.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Last night, Yanagisawa-kun contacted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:41.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He insisted the festival club wasn't what we thought it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and asked to meet with me to clear up any misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:48.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana abandoned our club's preparations and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The upperclassmen were furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't need to mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:57.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After seeing the video he put together of your club practicing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,we changed our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The festival club is doing its best to perform the Awa dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:07.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was a mistake for us to break our promise to assist you at the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I reached out to my contacts and got these instruments together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We brought outfits, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, will you let us play for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:23.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She told me what's going on with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was losing sight of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was able to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll always be watching you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and waiting for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come home anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:06.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:12.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go, festival club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The present is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, countless versions of our past selves
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,are always crying, laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:55.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,falling in love, getting hurt, joking around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,feeling happy, and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,These feelings are born all the time, and in the next moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,they become the past and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:18.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But the truth is, everyone's time is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:25.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right after it's born, every moment becomes the past and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But... I'm alive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:39.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can see this moment, the present, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:44.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right now... isn't that everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After that, I returned to my former self...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:55.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...and lost all my memories since the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:15.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're wrong, I'm telling you you're wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, you still don't notice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Though I've wanted to touch that arm for the past two or three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:28.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:38.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The urge to scream is so great that, look, I can't stand it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So why, why won't you notice even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:51.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you really, really in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't need words of flattery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Love me semi-eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:04.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After 5,000 years or so, I won't be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not endless
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:10.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I will die someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:17.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Being told "I'll love you forever" won't make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First, think only that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:25.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll love me till I die
